metadata.name: Mystery of the Empty Room
metadata.description:
A huge room, locked, empty and only two doors. One big and one small, padlocked. A giant palace that has been several things and is now touristy, however, full of macabre and ancient stories of lives that passed through there and some stayed there.

Some souls, wander in its great halls and say that it is possible to hear voices and objects falling during winter nights.
